text: Dneprovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakibashevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 80 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 14 km from Anyasevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Dneprovka
